                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/10299" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-2602</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">281 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">破茧成蝶：瑞声科技的声光技术生态战略转型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Cocoon into a butterfly: AAC Technologies&#39; sound and light technology ecological strategy transformation</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">尹志军，杨倩，刘霞</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">河北工业大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">瑞声科技控股有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">电子工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">12 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">瑞声科技；战略转型；智能工厂；技术复用；多维场景布局</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">AAC Technologies、Strategic Transformation、Smart Factory、Technology Reuse、Multi-dimensional Scene Layout</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例描述了瑞声科技突破行业周期困境的战略转型之路。作为全球消费电子声学元器件龙头企业，瑞声科技早期凭借市场机遇快速崛起，通过持续技术创新巩固行业地位。然而2018年后遭遇结构化挑战：需求端受制于智能手机市场增长放缓，供给端面临产业链成本挤压，导致净利润连续下滑的六年经营危机。在此背景下，瑞声通过“三位一体”战略实现突破：智能制造体系重构生产效能、核心技术复用与协同创新、应用场景横向延伸。2024年净利润同比增长142.7%，经营性现金流恢复至2016年峰值水平，标志其成功实现从“声学器件供应商”向“智能感知解决方案商”的价值跃迁。 本案例不仅为传统制造企业破解“技术孤岛－场景局限－利润陷阱”困境提供了可复制的转型范式，揭示通过核心技术弹性扩展与场景生态进化构建企业第二增长曲线的路径，也有助于学员深入理解高端制造企业在复杂产业环境中的战略响应与执行过程，提升对技术创新、生态布局与战略重构的综合决策能力。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">This case study describes the strategic transformation of AAC Technologies, which broke through the industry cycle predicament. As a leading global provider of acoustic components for consumer electronics, AAC Technologies rapidly rose to prominence in the early days by seizing market opportunities and solidified its position through continuous technological innovation. However, since 2018, it has faced structural challenges: on the demand side, it was constrained by the slowdown in the growth of the smartphone market; on the supply side, it was squeezed by rising costs in the supply chain, leading to a six-year operating crisis with consecutive declines in net profit. Against this backdrop, AAC achieved a breakthrough through a &quot;three-in-one&quot; strategy: reconfiguring the production efficiency of the intelligent manufacturing system, reusing and innovating core technologies in a coordinated manner, and horizontally extending application scenarios. In 2024, its net profit increased by 142.7% year-on-year, and its operating cash flow returned to the peak level of 2016, marking its successful transition from an &quot;acoustic component supplier&quot; to an &quot;intelligent perception solution provider&quot;. This case not only provides a replicable transformation model for traditional manufacturing enterprises to break through the &quot;technology island - scenario limitation - profit trap&quot; predicament, revealing the path to building a second growth curve through the flexible expansion of core technologies and the evolution of the scenario ecosystem, but also helps learners deeply understand the strategic response and execution process of high-end manufacturing enterprises in complex industrial environments, and enhance their comprehensive decision-making capabilities in technological innovation, ecological layout, and strategic reconstruction.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《企业战略管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">竞争战略；增长战略；战略转型的内外部因素；动态能力理论；</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-12</td>
                            </tr>
